snippet.title: Amber Heard's Small Birth Family
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is a young Hollywood actress and a stunning model  whose professional career gains momentum due to extraordinary roles in movies and not only. She dreamt of becoming a famous film performer and in order to make this dream come true, she worked hard to pay for portfolio as well as filming in the studio. At 16, Amber moved to New York to start modeling career. Her bright beauty and beautiful body let her reach success without putting much effort. With the time, modeling sphere began weighing down and Heard moved to LA to “conquer” the Hollywood. She started from playing bit roles in various projects such as The O.C. and Jack and Bobby. However, even these minor roles, helped her to get certain success and she was noticed by many film directors. In such a way, she can be seen in Friday Night Lights, North Country, Never Back Down, Pineapple Express, Magic Mike XXL and so many other works.

Amber’s father David is an actor in his own right. Knowing how hard an actor’s life is, he never wanted a daughter to be involved in the filmmaking industry. Nonetheless, it was Amber’s dream and she followed it. Later, David admitted that she made the right decision and is very proud of her. Both father and daughter can be seen at different events and on a red carpet together.

Meanwhile, a mother Paige is an IT person, who creates websites. In accordance with the actress, her mother is the best parent she could have ever had. Paige has always been supporting the daughter as well as taught her many things in life. 

The stunning movie star has a younger sister named Whitney, who is also an actress. Both sisters are extremely close and are often seen together at different parties and events. Nothing much is known about Whitney’s personal life, but there is a rumor that she is dating an actor Ryan Adams. 

That is all.
Don’t forget to subscribe to our channel.
